    • networkProtocolVersion

      public NetworkRegistry.ChannelBuilder networkProtocolVersion(Supplier<String> networkProtocolVersion)
      The impl protocol string for this channel. This will be gathered during login and sent to the remote partner, where it will be tested with against the relevant predicate.
      参数:
      networkProtocolVersion - A supplier of strings for impl protocol version testing

    • clientAcceptedVersions

      public NetworkRegistry.ChannelBuilder clientAcceptedVersions(Predicate<String> clientAcceptedVersions)
      A predicate run on the client, with the networkProtocolVersion(Supplier) string from the server, or the special value NetworkRegistry.ABSENT indicating the absence of the channel on the remote side.
      参数:
      clientAcceptedVersions - A predicate for testing
      返回:
      the channel builder
